features: PACKING CUBES MAKE TRAVEL EASIER-Compression cubes help you with packing your clothes for upcoming trips by compressing the air out of them. Save up to 30% more space in your suitcase!

LUGGAGE ORGANIZER- See through mesh makes organization easy. Keep different outfits in separate compression cubes and always be ready for what’s next! Easily pack away clothing like raincoats/heavier jackets that are not used as often.

HOW MUCH DOES EXTRA LARGE SET HOLD? Extra Large packing cube holds approx 3 Mens Large Tshirts, Large puffy jacket, 2 long sleeve large shirts, one pair jeans, one pair mens pants. Large compression cube holds 2 mens tshirts, 1 pair mens pants, and 2 long sleeve shirts. Small compression cube holds about 8 womens shirts. Shoe Bag is a great junk drawer-electronics, toiletries, underwear or swimsuits. Laundry bag is great for dirty clothes or a beach bag.

USE EXPANDED OR COMPRESSED- Use these like normal packing cubes when you need to pack more. Packing less? Use the compression zipper to save even more space! Extra Large Dimensions Compressed size: 15.7x11x4in Large Dimensions Compressed size: 14x10x1in Expanded Size: 14x10x4in Small Dimensions Compressed size 10x7x1in Expanded Size: 10x7x4in

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Went a little nuts trying a TON of compression cubes for travel, this is by far the best I tried
reviews.reviewText: These compression packing cubes are sooo much better than many of the other ones I tested out.Why? Because of the superior materials that they are made with.The fine, very tough, smooth, and resilient mesh is the most important component: it is so translucent that is it practically clear, allowing you to easily see what clothes of yours are in each cube you pack. But since it is strong yet fine mesh, the clothes compact well and can still breathe to not get stale during travel.The rest of the materials used in the cube are also superior quality - ultra lightweight, whisper smooth and stitch seamed really well. So you can stuff them thoroughly, compress them easily, they add hardly any weight of their own, and the smooth material lets the packed cubes slither amongst each other in your suitcase or bag so the packed set settles down into its own most minimal pile.The zippers are great - strong, clean teeth and tough without being bulky.And the handles on the overall set are great.After trying several different kinds of cubes, many of which looked to be super similar to these Trippd ones - everyone in my family only wanted a set of these for themselves. No one wants to use the other ones that aren't as good for use. Either the family rejected other brands' cubes are too stiff, don't compress as well, you can't see what you packed inside the cube easily, they add unnecessary weight...or all of the above.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 4, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for staying organized!
reviews.reviewText: This set of packing cubes offers the same great quality you get in all of the Tripped Travel Gear products. The fabric is durable and the zippers are strong. The cubes are large enough to hold bulky or larger sized clothing and fit perfectly in a standard size suitcase. This set would be perfect for a ski trip or other cold weather vacation. I love the see-through mesh front so you can see exactly what is in each cube. I machine washed them in cold water, gentle cycle and hung them to dry and they came out looking great and smelling clean. The dusty teal color matches perfectly with my dusty teal toiletry kit so I am now organized and coordinated! I would love to see this same style of packing cubes in a smaller carry-on bag size. Thanks Tripped Travel Gear for another great product!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best travel accessory I have ever bought.
reviews.reviewText: One of the best travel accessories I have purchased in a long time. Most packing cubes that I have used in the past are not of a compression style, these are easy to load and then simple to zip down for compression. The zippers are smooth with no tendency to catch on the material. I found the sizes to be just right with the larger ones fitting nicely in a carry on spinner bag. The material seems to be tear resistant but yet is light and translucent enough to see what is inside.I did initially question the handles, to me that seemed to be a useless feature that would take up space. But they are convenient when you want to grab several tubes at one time.The laundry bag is a great idea as well.Great kit with good features and a perfect selection of sizes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Everything they say these are!
reviews.reviewText: Terrific packing cubes that compress the contents to allow more room in luggage. I especially like that you can see through them at a glance to see what’s in them. I had previously bought a different brand that was described as being see-through, but really wasn’t - these actually are. Also really like the different sizes being offered in this set, and the bag for dirty laundry. Cubes are attractive, and look like they’re well-made. Hoping they’ll last many years. By the way, this type of compression cube does not completely remove all air, like the familiar clear plastic zip packing/storage bags. The good thing about that is they don’t smash and wrinkle your clothing like those vacuum bags - I didn’t need to press anything.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I like this so much I bought 3
reviews.reviewText: I haven't traveled with it yet - but I really this. It's pricey, but it's good quality. Nice to look at, nice material. I previously tried another less expensive brand, and that look and felt cheap - sort of loud and crunchy. Can definitely shove quite a bit into these when the cube is expanded and then you compress down by zippering up the second zipper. It doesn't compress like a vacuum sealed bag or anything, but you do definitely save some space. And it keeps stuff organized. I'm packing for a trip right now and can put all my tshirts in one, pants in another, etc. And it's sheer so you know what's what.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent choice for travel organization!
reviews.reviewText: I am so happy I purchased this set of travel bags! They made my trip to Minnesota a breeze! I was staying at a few different locations and I was able to easily sort my bulky clothes neatly in my suitcase.A few features that were extra handy:- I like that you can see into the bag when it is completely zipped. It made it easier for me to remember which bag was for which location. I could also survey all my options without forgetting what I packed!- The compression zipper being a different color is a game changer! I always knew I was pulling on the correct zipper!- The laundry bag was amazing! Kept sweaty garments away from the rest of my suitcase, and since the clothes were all together, it made my trip to the washing machine a breeze!- These bags were great straight out of the packaging. I'm incredibly sensitive to smells and this product didn't have any chemical smells when I got it out of the shipping box. I also didn't experience any smells on my clothes after using the bags!I have only used them for two trips, so I can't comment on longevity, but I think these bags are a win if you are looking for a quality travel bag with a compression option!
Highly recommend, strong, lightweight and zippers are very strong.

After years of travelling, I discovered these compression packs recently & they were the best thing I took on a 2 month holiday to Europe. I ironed everything before putting into packs and they kept my clothes organised with minimal creasing. Although the sizes initially looked small, they fitted perfectly into my suitcase and anything bigger would have made my bags too heavy. They're also great in carry-on bags to keep your clothes neat & tidy. I have recommended them to all my friends plus they're a great present.
